    metaDescription: "Understand Land Registry requirements for development finance. Title registration, restrictions, charges and boundary issues all covered. Get expert help today.",
    excerpt: "Land Registry records underpin every development finance transaction. This guide explains how title registration works, what lenders check, common title issues that cause delays, and how to resolve them before they become problems.",
    category: "legal",
    datePublished: "2026-02-09",
