    metaDescription: "Rights of way and easements can complicate development finance. Learn how to identify, manage and resolve access issues on your site. Expert guidance available.",
    excerpt: "Easements and rights of way are among the most complex title issues affecting development sites. This guide explains the different types of rights, how they impact your scheme design, and what lenders require before releasing funds.",
