    metaTitle: "Permitted Development Rights Finance | UK Guide",
    metaDescription: "Finance office-to-residential and commercial conversions under permitted development rights. Prior approval, Class MA, lender requirements and costs explained.",
    excerpt: "Permitted development rights allow certain commercial-to-residential conversions without full planning permission. This guide explains which conversions qualify, the prior approval process, and how to secure development finance for PD schemes.",
    category: "legal",
    datePublished: "2026-02-09",
